Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:11.44,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Suiko, would you tell me what's \Ngoing on in this building?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:15.15,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Tetsu and Asaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.04,0:00:18.83,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me, and you'll understand everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.42,0:00:21.08,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to fight to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:24.58,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You're my teammate. I know your ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:29.09,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? My ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.84,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun talking to you, \Nbut could we cut to the chase?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.36,0:00:48.61,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That seems to be a creepy, disquieting deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:51.54,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,It pleases me that you catch on quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:53.52,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,The name of this deck's clan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:56.03,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,...Link Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:01.37,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Link Joker...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.78,0:02:45.39,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Link Joker. This is the first \NI've heard of that clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:49.86,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,It has the power to outmatch \Nall the other clans around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:54.03,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,It's the ultimate forbidden clan, \Nand depending on how you use it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:56.34,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,it's even possible to obtain infinite power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:58.65,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That's Link Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:01.53,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You're really a cheerleader \Nfor this clan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:08.29,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting with this deck \Nmakes me feel ecstatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:13.92,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,The reason is that... \NI'll be able to beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:18.41,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You feel it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:20.54,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Link Joker's magnificence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.23,0:03:26.68,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You're dying to find out what \Nkind of power this deck holds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:33.00,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You've fallen under the \Nspell of its power, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:41.01,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,And it seems that the only way I can look \Nfor Tetsu and Asaka is by fighting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:46.99,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Clouds Over Fukuhara High School
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:50.58,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come here to defeat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:54.28,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I did... and I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.55,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,My former master was monitoring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.96,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,My current master craves your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:02.97,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Your master, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:05.90,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That strange feeling I sensed from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.97,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's the reason I found it \Nhard to discern your true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:10.99,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Say what you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.99,0:04:13.60,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,There's my master, and then there's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:17.48,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:21.49,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we get this over with?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:24.98,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsu Shinjou... Asaka Narumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:27.49,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that worried about those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:31.58,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,It's because they're my teammates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:34.03,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they would \Nappreciate your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.93,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:42.57,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Beginning now, you're going to \Nlearn the various sides of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:45.84,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you know will be overturned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.26,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,...Reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:50.78,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing that won't change!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:52.13,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Can we just get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:59.27,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I'll understand everything after \Nfighting that deck, Link Joker, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.40,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:11.53,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! There's no end!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.53,0:05:13.42,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,What's with these guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:16.79,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! More of 'em?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:19.77,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,This darn necktie...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:22.36,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to move with \Nthis stupid uniform on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.95,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, Vanguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.95,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up the Vanguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.90,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Micro-hole Dracokid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:37.31,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Frontline Revenger, Claudas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:42.51,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, this is the first \Ntime I've seen this clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:46.60,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Despair comes to all who \Ngaze upon Link Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:50.86,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Ride! Gravity Ball Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.09,0:05:58.46,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I ride Nullity Revenger, Masquerade!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:03.76,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Claudas moves. Call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:06.34,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:12.46,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:20.19,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,The wait is over. I'll show \Nyou the power of Link Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:24.02,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Ride! Gravity Collapse Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.82,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Gravity Collapse Dragon's skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:35.90,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,When Gravity Ball Dragon is in the Soul, \NGravity Collapse gets +10000 power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:37.41,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:41.32,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,When I ride this unit on \Ntop of Gravity Ball Dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:44.59,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I can lock one of my \Nopponent's rear-guard units!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:46.17,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Lock...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:03.63,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Lock... It's the ultimate binding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:09.65,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,The spell won't be lifted until \Nthe end of your next turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:16.27,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You can't move; you can't attack;\N you can't even retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:18.54,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,All you can do is float there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:22.29,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,This is Link Joker...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.98,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That was just an introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:27.30,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,No more than a taste of what's to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:29.73,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:35.05,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,This looks like it'll be kind of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:43.73,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,All right. It won't get drenched \Nfrom the rain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:44.91,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:49.96,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,After the trouble I went \Nthrough to get a uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:52.82,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk! Treat other people's \Nthings with respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:08:00.58,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one who stirred \Nup the club members?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:04.21,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I did... and I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:07.28,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You've actually already \Nrealized it, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:11.28,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Those people... this deck... \Nthe otherworldly power...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:13.72,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because of something \Nmuch greater than any of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.37,0:08:15.45,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:19.85,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. This is all Void's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:21.89,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Void.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:29.46,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,A transcendent existence that takes \Nin everything with its darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:31.39,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,and returns all life to nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:37.08,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Void will swallow up not only the planet \NCray, but everything in existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:40.04,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That includes the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:45.77,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,By Reversing Earth's Vanguard fighters \Nand turning them into its own,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:49.76,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,the Earth will destroy \Nitself, along with Cray!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:51.13,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,"Reverse"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:57.54,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,All those who lose a fight against a \NLink Joker deck also lose their own will,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:59.87,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,and become one with Link Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:06.38,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That's "Reverse."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:11.71,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Fighters who lose to Reversed \Nfighters become Reversed themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:15.40,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Link Joker is becoming more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:20.21,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,People who lose are Reversed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:27.21,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That includes the club \Nmembers who challenged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.93,0:09:33.97,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break! There's no way you \Npunks could beat Kyou the Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:36.97,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't go around the world \Nten times over for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.25,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Seven times, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:40.14,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe seven and a half...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:43.16,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Whichever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:45.73,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,A bluff works better with a bigger number!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:48.68,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,What about Tetsu and Asaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:52.01,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... why don't you see \Nwith your own eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:58.91,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten serious at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:03.05,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,This is the mode I want \Nfrom you, Ren Suzugamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:09.84,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,If you join us, Link Joker \Nwill become even stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:13.80,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. When this fight is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:17.90,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,you'll also become one with \NLink Joker, body and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:20.60,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be Reversed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:38.65,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Two sides of the same coin, both \Ngood and evil reside within your blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:40.16,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I ride...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:46.09,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,...Blaster Dark Revenger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:50.52,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Blaster Dark's Counterblast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:54.26,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,When my Vanguard has "Revenger" in its name,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:56.80,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I can retire one of your \Nfront row rear-guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:00.43,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Gamma Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.25,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Doreen's skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:07.64,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,When Blaster Dark appears in the same column,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:10.53,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I can turn over one unit in the Damage Zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:16.90,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Blaster Dark's skill can \Nhold out against Link Joker's lock?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:19.87,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,If so, you're badly mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:24.91,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You need to get a better understanding \Nof just how fearsome Link Joker is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:26.14,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:28.66,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Call.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:31.20,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Knight of Nullity, Masquerade.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:33.42,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Masquerade attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.34,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:41.05,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Blaster Dark Revenger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:50.57,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:55.06,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,And Transient Revenger's lock opens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:08.54,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,From your expression, you seem to think \Nthat getting one unit locked is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:14.67,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you the true power of \Nthe ultimate clan, Link Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:19.30,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon of darkness, born of dark flames...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:23.15,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Convey an unending nightmare \Nto those who incur my wrath!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:26.58,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I ride Schwarzschild Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:34.64,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Schwarzschild Dragon's Counterblast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:39.94,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I look at the top five cards of my deck, \Nand if Schwarzschild Dragon is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.44,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I can add it to my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:46.34,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,And if Gravity Collapse Dragon is in the \NSoul, Schwarzschild gets +1000 power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:47.69,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Call.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:53.87,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Furious Claw Star-vader, Niobium. \NGravity Collapse Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:57.89,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Devour the same soul, become \Nthe dragon king of darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:12:59.63,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,and release your roar of destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:02.01,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Limit Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:07.64,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Schwarzschild Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:11.97,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I can lock three of my \Nopponent's rear-guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.12,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Lock three units?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:23.38,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Link Joker Limit Break?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:26.09,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Niobium and Lanthanum's skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:31.04,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,They get +2000 power for every \Nlocked rear-guard of my opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:34.03,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,With three locked units, \Nthat's a total of 6000.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:42.30,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,The more I lock, the more power I gain,\N while my opponent loses power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:44.76,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,This is Link Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:49.51,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You understand how wonderful \Nit is, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:52.34,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You've fallen to the dark side before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:54.29,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,With you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:59.21,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Even the great Ren Suzugamori \Nis shaken and scared
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:03.02,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,when faced with the power of Link Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:08.12,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,But that weakness will be wiped away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:10.03,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,When you're Reversed, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:13.31,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need that kind of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:18.04,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how long that tough talk will last.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:25.05,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you manage to ride out this turn, \Nyou'll only be able to attack once next turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:29.38,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Gravity Collapse Dragon attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:37.14,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Schwarzschild Dragon attacks \Nwith a boost from Lanthanum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:41.90,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect guard with Dark Revenger, Mac Lir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.65,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Niobium attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:47.76,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:52.96,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn, but you can only attack once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:54.70,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:59.95,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Considering the situation, no one would \Ncriticize you if you forfeited the game here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:03.76,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I would criticize myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:10.09,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't help Tetsu and Asaka, there was \Nno point in our forming a team together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:13.66,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Team? What are you talking about \Nat this stage of the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:17.89,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,When we formed a team, I decided \Nthat I would protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:23.86,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I'm prepared to put my own \Nlife on the line for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:34.20,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Then I think I'll see just \Nhow prepared you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:40.08,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I ride Illusionary Revenger, Mordred Phantom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:44.92,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:47.92,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Guard! Intercept!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:54.74,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:04.60,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Even with the locks undone, your \Ndespair-inducing disadvantage doesn't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:09.25,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I like those eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:10.13,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:13.11,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Your useless resistance is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:14.33,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:17.12,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I attack your rear-guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:22.25,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I attack your Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:23.56,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.83,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I attack once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:28.88,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:33.88,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:40.50,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Well done. But as a result of that guarding, \Nyou only have one card in your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:43.52,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to block my next attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:49.29,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, I've got all these cards \Nin my hand, and an intercept unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:51.90,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if you'll be able \Nto get an attack through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:56.93,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, remember? I'm prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:00.49,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Final Turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:07.47,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Tremble in fear in the \Nface of even greater rage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:09.84,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Break ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:17.68,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Revenger, Raging Form Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:21.64,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,The Vanguard gets +10000 power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:26.77,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I can superior call a grade 2 or lower\N Shadow Paladin from my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:29.27,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Nullity Revenger, Masquerade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:32.28,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,And it gets +5000 power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:34.09,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:35.81,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:39.03,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Transient Revenger attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:43.04,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,With its skill, it gets +3000 power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:49.06,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Raging Form Dragon attacks \Nwith a boost from Doreen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:52.06,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Raging Form Dragon's Counterblast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:54.82,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,+3000 power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:18:00.09,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect guard with Barrier \NStar-vader, Promethium.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:04.78,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Drive trigger check.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:12.76,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you got multiple \Nbreak rides... Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:15.47,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Your last hope is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:17.38,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:21.47,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Endless wrath...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:24.58,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Even when your body changes, your soul carries on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:26.08,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Be reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:30.52,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Revenger, Raging Form Dragon's Limit Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:36.50,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,When the attack is over, I can \Nretire three of your rear-guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:45.32,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Superior persona ride with the Revenger, \NRaging Form Dragon unit in my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:47.80,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,And it gets +10000 power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:52.28,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Raging Form Dragon stands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:54.04,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:58.34,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Wrathful dragon, pulverize \Nthem with your brutal roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:03.36,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that Limit Break, \Nhe's got two more attacks left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:06.28,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I have a damage of... 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:10.12,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,As long as he doesn't draw a \Ntrigger, I can protect myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:12.22,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,No guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.70,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,He's confident that he'll draw a trigger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:24.88,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Drive trigger... check.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:31.52,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Second check.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:44.48,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Critical trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:48.04,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I give the +5000 power \Nto Illusionary Revenger
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:50.67,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,and the extra critical to Raging Form.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.07,0:20:04.16,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think he'd draw a trigger there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:19.96,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Ren Suzugamori... You're stronger \Nthan I had imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:27.66,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You're up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.45,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you're back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:39.74,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Now I know at least one way to \Ndeal with this weird situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:44.97,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,The Reversed fighter has to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:47.29,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:51.22,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Suiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:53.71,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:58.41,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,When I made that vow to put my life on \Nthe line, I didn't just mean for those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:00.98,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I meant everyone on the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:08.75,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Suiko went to their side...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:17.34,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,No good. It's not only Kourin and Rekka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:19.38,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get through to Aichi either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:22.96,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Some kind of strong force is at work...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:26.96,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsu... Asaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:34.36,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi, what are you daydreaming about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:38.42,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I know what it is. You're thinking \Nabout Kourin, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:41.72,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You said she hasn't been going \Nto school at all lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:45.95,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Right. But I heard she's just busy, \Nso I'm not worried any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:49.05,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Easy for you to say! You at least \Ngo to the same school she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.05,0:21:54.41,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,All I can do is come here to Card Capital \Nevery day in the hopes of seeing her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:58.58,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,What is... this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.75,0:22:05.97,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.48,0:22:08.68,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:10.33,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Asaka's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:21.14,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Asaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.89,0:24:00.08,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,So fighters who lose to Reversed fighters \Nthemselves become Reversed...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.53,0:24:02.99,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I think that's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.99,0:24:04.03,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.75,0:24:07.79,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember who Reversed you, Suiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.13,0:24:09.34,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:11.39,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,The Reversed fighters are increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.39,0:24:15.09,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Secretly and out of sight, but surely.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.45,0:24:17.35,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Eternal Marionette!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.05,0:24:24.94,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal Marionette!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.84,0:24:21.06,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Who will be the next person \Nto be menaced by Link Joker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.06,0:24:22.81,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please be safe!